  <brief_title>Feasibility Testing of a Novel Endoscope for Reflectance Confocal Microscopy of Normal Oral Tissue In Vivo</brief_title>
  <official_title>Feasibility Testing of a Novel Endoscope for Reflectance Confocal Microscopy of Normal Oral Tissue In Vivo</official_title>
