  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to obtain images (pictures) of normal oral tissue, which occur
      inside the mouth, using a special camera. These pictures will be used in our research to
      evaluate a new technology that uses a laser and takes pictures of the microscopic structure
      of tissue. The technology is called &quot;reflectance confocal microscopy.&quot;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
